text: Praful Khoda Patel is a former Member of Legislative assembly from Himatnagar constituency in Gujarat for its 12th legislative assembly (2007â€“12). He also was MoS Home Minister of Gujarat. He has been the Administrator of Daman and Diu and as the Administrator of Dadra and Nagar Haveli. In December 2020, he became Administrator of Lakshadweep following the death of Dineshwar Sharma. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Administrators of Lakshadweep Category:Administrators of Dadra and Nagar Haveli
